prompt: A macro close-up shot of a steaming, dark roast coffee in a ceramic mug, with scattered coffee beans creating a textured foreground. The background features a soft sunrise with golden hour light gently illuminating the scene, enhancing the rich texture and aroma. Emphasize the intricate details of the coffee crema and the condensation on the mug.
